Sorry.

24
00:01:54,501 --> 00:01:56,540
I'm just giving you
some friendly advice.

25
00:01:56,620 --> 00:01:57,661
To be honest,

26
00:01:58,781 --> 00:02:00,581
I don't like advice.

27
00:02:00,980 --> 00:02:02,301
Master, don't worry.

28
00:02:02,540 --> 00:02:04,180
Every single member of my team and I

29
