After all, the layoff compensation
is more attractive.

31
00:02:07,661 --> 00:02:08,661
Don't you think so?

32
00:02:09,341 --> 00:02:10,941
Alright. If there's nothing else,

33
00:02:11,061 --> 00:02:12,421
I'll get back to work

34
