Mei Chengyi, I haven't finished.

36
00:02:16,501 --> 00:02:17,501
Mei Chengyi.

37
00:02:20,941 --> 00:02:22,300
You!

38
00:02:23,420 --> 00:02:24,420
I'm furious.

39
00:02:36,621 --> 00:02:37,661
