(A Second Chance)
Xiao, good morning.

44
00:03:55,901 --> 00:03:56,901
Morning.

45
00:04:14,980 --> 00:04:16,340
Would you like some?

46
00:04:16,420 --> 00:04:17,780
No need. I don't need it.

47
00:04:17,860 --> 00:04:19,180
I-I've already eaten.

48
00:04:19,901 --> 00:04:20,901
You go ahead.

49
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:22,940
Alright.

50
00:04:28,661 --> 00:04:29,661
Wang Ke.

51
00:04:30,380 --> 00:04:31,100
Nothing annoying,

52
00:04:31,180 --> 00:04:32,180
