No.

54
00:04:34,141 --> 00:04:35,380
Everything is good.

55
00:04:36,420 --> 00:04:37,420
What's wrong?

56
00:04:38,540 --> 00:04:39,221
Nothing.

57
00:04:39,301 --> 00:04:40,500
You go ahead.

58
00:04:41,781 --> 00:04:42,781
It's quite nice.

59
00:05:20,701 --> 00:05:22,500
Where is she going?

60
00:05:23,021 --> 00:05:24,461
After so long time,

61
