Going this far?

64
00:05:35,420 --> 00:05:36,461
Who cares?

65
00:05:36,821 --> 00:05:37,821
Keep following,

66
00:05:37,901 --> 00:05:39,380
and we'll know then.

67
00:05:48,740 --> 00:05:50,581
This apartment is good.

68
00:05:53,540 --> 00:05:55,581
But we have to

69
00:05:56,021 --> 00:05:58,221
