Pay the down payment first.

72
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:05,661
If you're worried about the loan,

73
00:06:05,741 --> 00:06:07,380
I have pension.

74
00:06:08,101 --> 00:06:10,100
If I break up with Mei Chengyi,

75
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:12,620
