00:40:12,381 --> 00:40:12,781
What?

894
00:40:12,861 --> 00:40:13,620
She shouted at me.

895
00:40:13,700 --> 00:40:14,501
Didn't you hear?

896
00:40:14,581 --> 00:40:15,501
I didn't hear it.

897
00:40:15,581 --> 00:40:16,581
She is my girlfriend.

898
00:40:18,260 --> 00:40:19,220
You have dated not long,

899
00:40:19,300 --> 00:40:20,700
and you're protecting her?

900
00:40:21,220 --> 00:40:21,982
What else then?

901
00:40:22,062 --> 00:40:23,140
To protect you?

902
00:40:24,021 --> 00:40:24,862
Let me tell you.

903
00:40:24,942 --> 00:40:26,300
Qian Xiaomi.

904
00:40:26,581 --> 00:40:27,941
Let go of me.

905
00:40:31,381 --> 00:40:32,381
I'm warning you.

906
00:40:32,461 --> 00:40:33,302
Starting today,

907
00:40:33,382 --> 00:40:34,901
you can't see my kids anymore.

908
00:40:35,581 --> 00:40:36,780
They have the surname Qian.

909
00:40:37,021 --> 00:40:37,981
Their grandma is sick.

910
00:40:38,061 --> 00:40:39,660
Why can't they stay in the hospital?

911
00:40:39,740 --> 00:40:41,140
When Dami was sick,

912
00:40:41,260 --> 00:40:42,220
where were you

913
00:40:42,300 --> 00:40:43,300
and this grandma?

914
00:40:43,736 --> 00:40:44,661
When Xiaomi was a baby,

915
00:40:44,661 --> 00:40:46,180
crying all night long,

916
00:40:46,260 --> 00:40:46,862
Dami and I

917
00:40:46,942 --> 00:40:48,060
went to the hospital.

918
00:40:48,140 --> 00:40:49,461
Where were you two?

919
00:40:49,620 --> 00:40:50,700
You and the mistress

920
00:40:50,780 --> 00:40:51,981
tried hard to steal

921
00:40:52,061 --> 00:40:53,620
the house of me and the kids,

922
00:40:53,700 --> 00:40:55,861
had you ever thought
that their surname is Qian?

923
00:40:56,260 --> 00:40:57,461
Let me tell you, Qian Hao.

924
00:40:57,541 --> 00:40:58,660
These two kids

925
00:40:58,740 --> 00:40:59,941
were not born

926
00:41:00,021 --> 00:41:01,021
for your filial piety.

927
00:41:03,140 --> 00:41:05,140
If anything happens

928
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:06,780
to Xiaomi and Dami,

929
00:41:07,501 --> 00:41:08,981
I will make you pay with your life.

930
00:41:11,861 --> 00:41:12,861
Let's go.

931
00:41:15,620 --> 00:41:16,620
Move aside.

932
00:41:39,981 --> 00:41:40,981
Hello, honey.

933
00:41:41,901 --> 00:41:42,700
Xia Chungeng.

934
00:41:42,820 --> 00:41:43,861
Come home now!

935
00:41:43,941 --> 00:41:45,140
Now!

936
00:41:46,021 --> 00:41:47,180
What happened?

937
00:41:47,901 --> 00:41:48,701
I have a meeting

938
00:41:48,781 --> 00:41:49,821
to host.

939
00:41:49,901 --> 00:41:50,580
Okay.

940
00:41:50,660 --> 00:41:51,382
If you don't care

941
00:41:51,462 --> 00:41:53,060
about me and your sister fighting,

942
00:41:53,140 --> 00:41:54,501
don't come back.

943
00:41:59,340 --> 00:42:00,340
Turn around ahead.

944
00:42:00,461 --> 00:42:01,301
Go back to my house.

945
00:42:01,381 --> 00:42:02,181
Faster.

946
00:42:02,261 --> 00:42:03,501
Mr. Xia, the meeting...

947
00:42:03,861 --> 00:42:04,504
Take a leave.

948
00:42:04,504 --> 00:42:05,461
Okay.

949
00:42:05,541 --> 00:42:06,260
The meeting

950
00:42:06,340 --> 00:42:07,340
is not important now.

951
00:42:14,438 --> 00:42:15,780
The progesterone levels are good.

952
00:42:16,101 --> 00:42:17,941
The ultrasound
shows the embryo is stable.

953
00:42:18,941 --> 00:42:20,700
But you have uterine fibroids.

954
00:42:20,780 --> 00:42:22,061
This needs special attention.

955
00:42:22,740 --> 00:42:24,061
As the child gets bigger,

956
00:42:24,180 --> 00:42:25,821
the fibroids will grow

957
00:42:25,901 --> 00:42:26,941
affected by hormones.

958
00:42:27,021 --> 00:42:28,941
It will be easier
to cause friction bleeding.

959
00:42:29,101 --> 00:42:30,101
So,

960
00:42:30,541 --> 00:42:31,342
after six months,

961
00:42:31,422 --> 00:42:32,861
it's recommended to have bed rest.

962
00:42:32,980 --> 00:42:34,700
If you give birth,
go for a cesarean section

963
00:42:35,021 --> 00:42:36,581
and remove the fibroids.

964
00:42:38,140 --> 00:42:40,101
Doctor, I want to be discharged.

965
00:42:43,180 --> 00:42:44,180
Okay.

966
00:42:44,421 --> 00:42:45,941
I'll make you a discharge slip

967
00:42:46,021 --> 00:42:47,501
and give you the doctor's advices.

968
00:42:47,581 --> 00:42:48,022
Okay.

969
00:42:48,102 --> 00:42:49,941
Let the family handle it.

970
00:42:51,101 --> 00:42:52,101
Okay.

971
00:42:52,220 --> 00:42:53,220
Thank you.

972
00:42:54,541 --> 00:42:55,541
Thank you, doctor.

